                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</nav>

<!-- About Me Section -->
<section class="container my-5 text-white">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-md-8 text-center">
            <h2 class="mb-4">About Me</h2>
            <img src="~/images/profile.jpeg" alt="Profile Picture"
                 class="img-fluid rounded-circle mb-4 shadow" style="max-width: 200px;" />

            <p>
                Hello! I'm <strong>Heba Nagy</strong>, a passionate and detail-oriented web developer with a strong background in back-end development.
                I specialize in building scalable and secure web applications using <strong>.NET Core</strong> and the <strong>MVC architecture</strong>.
            </p>

            <p>
                I'm constantly learning and keeping up with the latest technologies to improve my skills and deliver high-quality software solutions.
                I enjoy solving complex problems and turning ideas into functional, user-friendly web experiences.
            </p>

            <p>
                When I’m not coding, I enjoy reading tech blogs, exploring UI/UX trends, and sometimes just relaxing with a good book or music 🎧📚.
            </p>

            <p>
                Feel free to explore my portfolio to see some of the projects I've worked on — each one tells a different story of creativity and technical growth.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Contact Section -->
<section class="container my-5 text-white">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-md-8">
            <h2 class="mb-4 text-center">Contact Me</h2>
            <div class="text-center mb-3">
                <p><i class="fas fa-envelope text-warning"></i> <a href="mailto:nagyheba537.com" class="text-white">heba@example.com</a></p>
                <p><i class="fab fa-linkedin text-warning"></i> <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/heba-nagy-a46744250/" class="text-white" target="_blank">linkedin.com/in/hebanagy</a></p>
                <p><i class="fab fa-github text-warning"></i> <a href="https://github.com/hebanagy15" class="text-white" target="_blank">github.com/hebanagy</a></p>
            </div>
            <form>
                <div class="mb-3">
                    <label for="name" class="form-label">Name</label>
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" id="name" placeholder="Your name">
                </div>
                <div class="mb-3">
                    <label for="email" class="form-label">Email</label>
                    <input type="email" class="form-control" id="email" placeholder="name@example.com">
                </div>
                <div class="mb-3">
                    <label for="message" class="form-label">Message</label>
                    <textarea class="form-control" id="message" rows="4" placeholder="Your message..."></textarea>
                </div>
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-warning">Send Message</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

